author: craigmcc
msg: Copy the DTDs for web application deployment descriptors to a new
"package" directory javax.servlet.resources, and the DTDs for tag
libraries and JSP pages in XML format to a new "package" directory
javax.servlet.jsp.resources.  This is consistent with the way that Swing
and several other Java packages deal with resource files, and will allow
applications that use the servlet.jar file created from this repository to
access the resources with ClassLoader.getResourceAsStream().
